Example questions
MT10 Apart from today, when was the last time you used a mobile phone to make a call, send an SMS, make a transaction or for any other activity?
Yesterday
In the past 7 days
In the past 30 days
In the past 90 days
More than 90 days ago
Never

FFI9. Apart from today, when was the last time you used a bank account for any financial activity?

FFI13.1. If you have to walk, how many minutes does it take you to get to the closest Over the counter in a branch of the bank or MFI from the place where you live?

MM16. Have you ever used a mobile money account to do the following ?: Receive wages for secondary job(s)

MM19_20. In the past 30 days, how many times did you use a mobile money account(s) for such financial activities? - Give a loan or receive payments on a loan

SFC1. On a scale from 0 (Extremely bad) to 10 (Extremely good), rate the choice of financial options that was available to you before you had access to a bank account.

IO1.3. In the past 90 days, how many times did you need to do the following ?  Transfer money between your m-money account and your bank account





